 tmux attach -t cluster_libpcap    # watch live
  tail -f clusters/libpcap_clustering.log   # check progress                                                       
  cat clusters/libpcap_state.json | python3 -m json.tool | head -20   # check state                                
   
  The state is saved to clusters/libpcap_state.json after every step, so even if the process crashes, you can see  
  how far it got. 